  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Certainty Level</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"abstract\" content=\"Indicate the reliability and therefore the likelihood of a flow in One Exposure from Operations.\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Indicate the reliability and therefore the likelihood of a flow in One Exposure from Operations.\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loioa20eeaef81d2478c8e75624c60b23a36\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Certainty Level</h1><div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Indicate the reliability and therefore the likelihood of a flow in One Exposure from Operations.</p>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Definition\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Definition</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"loioa20eeaef81d2478c8e75624c60b23a36__SMOJ_TSBSFFXR_CL\">This characteristic is used to indicate the reliability and therefore the likelihood of a flow in One Exposure\nfrom Operations. One Exposure derives cash forecasts for items from different sources. It stores this information with the certainty\nlevels.</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"loioa20eeaef81d2478c8e75624c60b23a36__section_hhx_p14_zkb\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n\n<p class=\"p\">If you select this checkbox, the dimension chosen is also relevant for aggregating the snapshot data of the specific data source.</p>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
